        </div>
        <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-1/4 h-1/4 opacity-10">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 200 200" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="text-yellow-600 w-full h-full">
                <path fill="currentColor" d="M46.3,-76.3C59.9,-68.5,70.9,-55.4,78,-40.3C85.1,-25.2,88.3,-8,86.1,8.2C83.8,24.4,76.1,39.8,65.2,52.3C54.3,64.9,40.2,74.6,24.5,79.7C8.7,84.8,-8.7,85.2,-23.2,79.2C-37.7,73.2,-49.4,60.7,-58.8,47.1C-68.2,33.5,-75.4,18.8,-78.1,2.7C-80.8,-13.4,-79,-31,-70.6,-44.2C-62.2,-57.4,-47.2,-66.1,-32.6,-73.2C-18,-80.3,-3.7,-85.7,9.9,-84.1C23.5,-82.5,46.9,-74,46.3,-76.3Z" transform="translate(100 100)" />
            </svg>
        </div>

        <!-- Branches d'olivier décorative -->
        <div class="absolute right-0 top-1/4 opacity-10 transform rotate-45 hidden lg:block">
            <svg width="200" height="200" viewBox="0 0 100 100" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="text-green-700">
                <g fill="currentColor">
                    <path d="M10,50 C20,30 40,40 50,50 C60,60 80,70 90,50" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1" fill="none"/>
                    <path d="M20,45 C25,40 30,42 25,47" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1" fill="none"/>
                    <path d="M30,52 C35,48 40,50 35,55" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1" fill="none"/>
                    <path d="M40,48 C45,43 50,45 45,50" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1" fill="none"/>
                    <path d="M55,52 C60,47 65,49 60,54" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1" fill="none"/>
                    <path d="M65,48 C70,43 75,45 70,50" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1" fill="none"/>
                    <path d="M75,53 C80,48 85,50 80,55" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1" fill="none"/>
                </g>
            </svg>
        </div>

        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10">
            <!-- En-tête de la page -->
            <div class="text-center mb-16">
                <h2 class="text-base font-semibold tracking-wide text-lime-600 uppercase">Échangeons ensemble</h2>
                <p class="mt-1 text-4xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 sm:text-5xl sm:tracking-tight">
                    Nous Contacter
                </p>
                <p class="max-w-xl mt-5 mx-auto text-xl text-gray-500">
                    Une question, une réservation ou une suggestion ? N'hésitez pas à nous contacter !
                </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Conteneur principal -->
            <div class="bg-white shadow-xl rounded-2xl overflow-hidden">
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2">

                    <!-- Colonne d'informations -->
                    <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-lime-600 to-lime-800 p-8 lg:p-12 text-white">
                        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">Nos Coordonnées</h3>

                        <!-- Informations de contact -->
                        <div class="space-y-8">
                            <div class="flex items-start">
                                <div class="flex-shrink-0">
                                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-lime-200" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z" />
                                    </svg>
                                </div>
                                <div class="ml-4">
                                    <p class="text-lg font-medium text-white">Téléphone</p>
                                    <p class="mt-1 text-lime-100">06 12 34 56 78</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <div class="flex items-start">
                                <div class="flex-shrink-0">
                                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-lime-200" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 8l7.89 5.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z" />
                                    </svg>
                                </div>
                                <div class="ml-4">
                                    <p class="text-lg font-medium text-white">Email</p>
                                    <p class="mt-1 text-lime-100">contact@saveursdevprovence.fr</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <div class="flex items-start">
                                <div class="flex-shrink-0">
                                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-lime-200" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17.657 16.657L13.414 20.9a1.998 1.998 0 01-2.827 0l-4.244-4.243a8 8 0 1111.314 0z" />
                                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 11a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" />
                                    </svg>
                                </div>
                                <div class="ml-4">
                                    <p class="text-lg font-medium text-white">Où nous trouver</p>
                                    <p class="mt-1 text-lime-100">Consultez notre calendrier de passage</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <div class="flex items-start">
                                <div class="flex-shrink-0">
                                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-lime-200" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
                                    </svg>
                                </div>
                                <div class="ml-4">
                                    <p class="text-lg font-medium text-white">Horaires</p>
                                    <div class="mt-1 text-lime-100">
                                        <p>Du Mardi au Samedi : 11h30 - 14h | 18h30 - 21h30</p>
                                        <p>Dimanche : 11h30 - 14h</p>
                                        <p>Lundi : Fermé</p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <!-- Réseaux sociaux -->
                        <div class="mt-12">
                            <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-white mb-4">Suivez-nous</h3>
                            <div class="flex space-x-4">
                                <a href="#" class="text-lime-100 hover:text-white transition-colors">
                                    <span class="sr-only">Facebook</span>
                                    <svg class="h-6 w-6" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
                                        <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M22 12c0-5.523-4.477-10-10-10S2 6.477 2 12c0 4.991 3.657 9.128 8.438 9.878v-6.987h-2.54V12h2.54V9.797c0-2.506 1.492-3.89 3.777-3.89 1.094 0 2.238.195 2.238.195v2.46h-1.26c-1.243 0-1.63.771-1.63 1.562V12h2.773l-.443 2.89h-2.33v6.988C18.343 21.128 22 16.991 22 12z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                                    </svg>
                                </a>
                                <a href="#" class="text-lime-100 hover:text-white transition-colors">
                                    <span class="sr-only">Instagram</span>
                                    <svg class="h-6 w-6" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
                                        <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M12.315 2c2.43 0 2.784.013 3.808.06 1.064.049 1.791.218 2.427.465a4.902 4.902 0 011.772 1.153 4.902 4.902 0 011.153 1.772c.247.636.416 1.363.465 2.427.048 1.067.06 1.407.06 4.123v.08c0 2.643-.012 2.987-.06 4.043-.049 1.064-.218 1.791-.465 2.427a4.902 4.902 0 01-1.153 1.772 4.902 4.902 0 01-1.772 1.153c-.636.247-1.363.416-2.427.465-1.067.048-1.407.06-4.123.06h-.08c-2.643 0-2.987-.012-4.043-.06-1.064-.049-1.791-.218-2.427-.465a4.902 4.902 0 01-1.772-1.153 4.902 4.902 0 01-1.153-1.772c-.247-.636-.416-1.363-.465-2.427-.047-1.024-.06-1.379-.06-3.808v-.63c0-2.43.013-2.784.06-3.808.049-1.064.218-1.791.465-2.427a4.902 4.902 0 011.153-1.772A4.902 4.902 0 015.45 2.525c.636-.247 1.363-.416 2.427-.465C8.901 2.013 9.256 2 11.685 2h.63zm-.081 1.802h-.468c-2.456 0-2.784.011-3.807.058-.975.045-1.504.207-1.857.344-.467.182-.8.398-1.15.748-.35.35-.566.683-.748 1.15-.137.353-.3.882-.344 1.857-.047 1.023-.058 1.351-.058 3.807v.468c0 2.456.011 2.784.058 3.807.045.975.207 1.504.344 1.857.182.466.399.8.748 1.15.35.35.683.566 1.15.748.353.137.882.3 1.857.344 1.054.048 1.37.058 4.041.058h.08c2.597 0 2.917-.01 3.96-.058.976-.045 1.505-.207 1.858-.344.466-.182.8-.398 1.15-.748.35-.35.566-.683.748-1.15.137-.353.3-.882.344-1.857.048-1.055.058-1.37.058-4.041v-.08c0-2.597-.01-2.917-.058-3.96-.045-.976-.207-1.505-.344-1.858a3.097 3.097 0 00-.748-1.15 3.098 3.098 0 00-1.15-.748c-.353-.137-.882-.3-1.857-.344-1.023-.047-1.351-.058-3.807-.058zM12 6.865a5.135 5.135 0 110 10.27 5.135 5.135 0 010-10.27zm0 1.802a3.333 3.333 0 100 6.666 3.333 3.333 0 000-6.666zm5.338-3.205a1.2 1.2 0 110 2.4 1.2 1.2 0 010-2.4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                                    </svg>
                                </a>
                                <a href="#" class="text-lime-100 hover:text-white transition-colors">
                                    <span class="sr-only">Twitter</span>
                                    <svg class="h-6 w-6" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
                                        <path d="M8.29 20.251c7.547 0 11.675-6.253 11.675-11.675 0-.178 0-.355-.012-.53A8.348 8.348 0 0022 5.92a8.19 8.19 0 01-2.357.646 4.118 4.118 0 001.804-2.27 8.224 8.224 0 01-2.605.996 4.107 4.107 0 00-6.993 3.743 11.65 11.65 0 01-8.457-4.287 4.106 4.106 0 001.27 5.477A4.072 4.072 0 012.8 9.713v.052a4.105 4.105 0 003.292 4.022 4.095 4.095 0 01-1.853.07 4.108 4.108 0 003.834 2.85A8.233 8.233 0 012 18.407a11.616 11.616 0 006.29 1.84"></path>
                                    </svg>
                                </a>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <!-- Carte simplifiée -->
                        <div class="mt-12 rounded-xl overflow-hidden">
                            <div class="aspect-w-16 aspect-h-9 relative">
                                <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center bg-lime-900/20">
                                    <img
                                            src="{{ asset('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1569336415962-a4bd9f69cd83?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1000&q=80') | default('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1569336415962-a4bd9f69cd83?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1000&q=80') }}"
                                            alt="Carte des emplacements"
                                            class="w-full h-full object-cover opacity-80"
                                    >
                                    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-lime-900/70 to-transparent"></div>
                                    <a href="#emplacement" class="absolute bottom-6 left-0 right-0 text-center text-white font-medium py-2 px-4 mx-auto w-max bg-lime-700 hover:bg-lime-600 rounded-full transition shadow-md">
                  <span class="flex items-center">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 mr-2" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
                      <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M5.05 4.05a7 7 0 119.9 9.9L10 18.9l-4.95-4.95a7 7 0 010-9.9zM10 11a2 2 0 100-4 2 2 0 000 4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                    </svg>
                    Voir notre calendrier de passage
                  </span>
                                    </a>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="p-8 lg:p-12">
                        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Envoyez-nous un message</h3>

                    {{ form_start(form, {'attr': {'class': 'space-y-6'}}) }}
                    <!-- Nom -->
                    <div>
                        {{ form_label(form.name, 'Nom', {'label_attr': {'class': 'block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700'}}) }}
                        <div class="mt-1">
                            {{ form_widget(form.name, {
                                'attr': {
                                    'class': 'py-3 px-4 block w-full shadow-sm focus:ring-lime-500 focus:border-lime-500 border-gray-300 rounded-md',
                                    'placeholder': 'Votre nom'
                                }
                            }) }}
                        </div>
                        {{ form_errors(form.name, {'attr': {'class': 'text-red-500 text-sm mt-1'}}) }}
                    </div>

                    <!-- Email -->
                    <div>
                        {{ form_label(form.email, 'Email', {'label_attr': {'class': 'block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700'}}) }}
                        <div class="mt-1">
                            {{ form_widget(form.email, {
                                'attr': {
                                    'class': 'py-3 px-4 block w-full shadow-sm focus:ring-lime-500 focus:border-lime-500 border-gray-300 rounded-md',
                                    'placeholder': 'votre.email@exemple.com'
                                }
                            }) }}
                        </div>
                        {{ form_errors(form.email, {'attr': {'class': 'text-red-500 text-sm mt-1'}}) }}
                    </div>

                    <!-- Téléphone -->
                    <div>
                        {{ form_label(form.phone, 'Téléphone', {'label_attr': {'class': 'block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700'}}) }}
                        <div class="mt-1">
                            {{ form_widget(form.phone, {
                                'attr': {
                                    'class': 'py-3 px-4 block w-full shadow-sm focus:ring-lime-500 focus:border-lime-500 border-gray-300 rounded-md',
                                    'placeholder': '06 XX XX XX XX'
                                }
                            }) }}
                        </div>
                        {{ form_errors(form.phone, {'attr': {'class': 'text-red-500 text-sm mt-1'}}) }}
                    </div>

                    <!-- Sujet -->
                    <div>
                        {{ form_label(form.subject, 'Sujet', {'label_attr': {'class': 'block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700'}}) }}
                        <div class="mt-1">
                            {{ form_widget(form.subject, {
                                'attr': {
                                    'class': 'py-3 px-4 block w-full shadow-sm focus:ring-lime-500 focus:border-lime-500 border-gray-300 rounded-md'
                                }
                            }) }}
                        </div>
                        {{ form_errors(form.subject, {'attr': {'class': 'text-red-500 text-sm mt-1'}}) }}
                    </div>

                    <!-- Message -->
                    <div>
                        {{ form_label(form.message, 'Message', {'label_attr': {'class': 'block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700'}}) }}
                        <div class="mt-1">
                            {{ form_widget(form.message, {
                                'attr': {
                                    'class': 'py-3 px-4 block w-full shadow-sm focus:ring-lime-500 focus:border-lime-500 border-gray-300 rounded-md',
                                    'rows': 6,
                                    'placeholder': 'Votre message...'
                                }
                            }) }}
                        </div>
                        {{ form_errors(form.message, {'attr': {'class': 'text-red-500 text-sm mt-1'}}) }}
                    </div>

                    <!-- Bouton Envoyer -->
                    <div>
                        <button type="submit" class="w-full inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 border border-transparent rounded-md shadow-sm text-base font-medium text-white bg-lime-600 hover:bg-lime-700 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-lime-500 transition">
                            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 mr-2" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
                                <path d="M10.894 2.553a1 1 0 00-1.788 0l-7 14a1 1 0 001.169 1.409l5-1.429A1 1 0 009 15.571V11a1 1 0 112 0v4.571a1 1 0 00.725.962l5 1.428a1 1 0 001.17-1.408l-7-14z" />
                            </svg>
                            Envoyer
                        </button>
                    </div>
                    {{ form_end(form) }}

                        <!-- Message de confiance -->
                        <div class="mt-8 flex items-center text-sm text-gray-500">
                            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-lime-500 mr-2" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
                                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M2.166 4.999A11.954 11.954 0 0010 1.944 11.954 11.954 0 0017.834 5c.11.65.166 1.32.166 2.001 0 5.225-3.34 9.67-8 11.317C5.34 16.67 2 12.225 2 7c0-.682.057-1.35.166-2.001zm11.541 3.708a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                            </svg>
                            <span>Nous respectons votre vie privée. Aucune donnée ne sera partagée.</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Témoignage -->
            <div class="mt-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-yellow-100 to-amber-100 rounded-2xl p-6 sm:p-10 shadow-md relative overflow-hidden">
                <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 -translate-y-1/4 translate-x-1/4 w-32 h-32 lg:w-40 lg:h-40 bg-yellow-400 opacity-20 rounded-full"></div>
                <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 translate-y-1/4 -translate-x-1/4 w-32 h-32 lg:w-40 lg:h-40 bg-lime-400 opacity-20 rounded-full"></div>

                <div class="relative">
                    <svg class="h-12 w-12 text-yellow-500 opacity-20 absolute -top-6 -left-2" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 32 32" aria-hidden="true">
                        <path d="M9.352 4C4.456 7.456 1 13.12 1 19.36c0 5.088 3.072 8.064 6.624 8.064 3.36 0 5.856-2.688 5.856-5.856 0-3.168-2.208-5.472-5.088-5.472-.576 0-1.344.096-1.536.192.48-3.264 3.552-7.104 6.624-9.024L9.352 4zm16.512 0c-4.8 3.456-8.256 9.12-8.256 15.36 0 5.088 3.072 8.064 6.624 8.064 3.264 0 5.856-2.688 5.856-5.856 0-3.168-2.304-5.472-5.184-5.472-.576 0-1.248.096-1.44.192.48-3.264 3.456-7.104 6.528-9.024L25.864 4z" />
                    </svg>

                    <p class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-medium text-gray-900 relative z-10">
                        "Notre food truck a été embauché pour un mariage et la nourriture était excellente. Tout le monde a adoré la pissaladière et la ratatouille. Service impeccable et équipe sympathique. Je recommande Saveurs de Provence sans hésitation !"
                    </p>

                    <div class="mt-6 sm:mt-8 flex items-center">
                        <div class="flex-shrink-0">
                            <img class="h-12 w-12 rounded-full" src="{{ asset('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1580489944761-15a19d654956?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&auto=format&fit=crop&w=256&q=80') | default('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1580489944761-15a19d654956?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&auto=format&fit=crop&w=256&q=80') }}" alt="Client satisfait">
                        </div>
                        <div class="ml-4">
                            <div class="text-base font-medium text-gray-900">Caroline Martin</div>
                            <div class="text-sm text-gray-600">Événement familial à Aix-en-Provence</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Section FAQ simplifiée -->
            <div class="mt-16">
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8 text-center">Questions Fréquentes</h3>

                <dl class="space-y-6 divide-y divide-gray-200">
                    <div class="pt-6">
                        <dt class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-900">
                            Faites-vous des événements privés ?
                        </dt>
                        <dd class="mt-2 text-base text-gray-500">
                            Oui, nous proposons nos services pour tous types d'événements : mariages, anniversaires, séminaires d'entreprise, etc. Contactez-nous pour un devis personnalisé.
                        </dd>
                    </div>

                    <div class="pt-6">
                        <dt class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-900">
                            Comment connaître vos emplacements ?
                        </dt>
                        <dd class="mt-2 text-base text-gray-500">
                            Nos emplacements sont régulièrement mis à jour sur notre page Facebook et Instagram. Vous pouvez également vous inscrire à notre newsletter pour recevoir notre planning hebdomadaire.
                        </dd>
                    </div>

                    <div class="pt-6">
                        <dt class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-900">
                            Proposez-vous des options végétariennes/véganes ?
                        </dt>
                        <dd class="mt-2 text-base text-gray-500">
                            Absolument ! Nous avons plusieurs options végétariennes à notre menu, dont notre ratatouille signature. Sur demande, nous pouvons également préparer des plats véganes.
                        </dd>
                    </div>
                </dl>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
{% endblock %}
